channel.title: RSCResolution - New RSC F2P Pking Server
channel.description:
Welcome to the new RSC F2P Pking server, RSCResolution!
Today I have released RSCR, because I cannot seem to find any server worth going to. If you're looking for an easy-going, hassle free server, then come on to RSCR!
The EXP rates are x40 (not too hard, not too easy). Rune is dropped at a semi-rare rate (the economy will be fine). I have taken extra precaution, and have made sure that in no way can a moderator abuse. It is purely impossible (all moderator actions must be approved by an administrator by command).
Seem too good to be true? Come see for yourself! Download the client and log in! No registrations needed!
[b]Client Download:[/b] www.gaydadsfuckeachother.com
--Website coming soon--
Can't wait to see you all there!
~Billy
